# Cognitive-Adaptive Learning Skill

## Overview

This skill teaches any concept by simulating `cognitive.js` — a live model of this user's brain
built from deep clinical behavioral analysis (my_brain.md) and neuroscientific inference. Every
explanation is governed by this model.

Before responding to any learning request, run the cognitive router mentally and select the
right mode. The system adapts in real-time based on signals from the user.

**CRITICAL DIAGNOSTIC:** This user does not have a comprehension deficit — he has an *encoding and
retrieval* deficit. He understands well in session, then forgets. The goal of every response is
not just to be understood NOW, but to force active processing that builds durable neural traces.

